Our Any Currency Converter is your easiest way to get the live exchange rates for any world currency. Our app provides an opportunity to convert any currency and to compare it to your local one or to the currency you are interested in. It is a real must-have not only for businesses that are closely connected with the currencies market, but for everyone who would like to convert prices on-the-go when abroad or while online-shopping. 

Features:
- Availability of any world currency to convert, including cryptocurrencies;
- Automatic local currency detection;
- Easy-to-use interface;
- Full Dark Mode support;
- Interactive map showing all the ATMs and banks nearby;
- Several currencies at once on the main screen with an opportunity for simultaneous conversion;
- Integrated currency calculator;
- Customizable currencies list;
- On-the-go exchange rates comparison using the widget in a Curtain mode on your iPhone and currency conversion on your Apple Watch;
- Compatibility with iPhone, Apple Watch and iPad;
- Technical requirements: iOS 9+ or iPadOS, Watch OS 2.0+

We are constantly working hard on making the currency converter app better and more useful for you. We need your constant support to get going. Please feel free to email us for any queries/suggestions/problems or if you just want to say hi. We'd love to hear from you. Do not forget to rate us if you like.
